          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>ðŸ’Ž Data Enrichment</h3>
          <p>
            ZoomInfo, Clearbit, and Apollo integration. Automate lead scoring, firmographic enrichment,
            and contact discovery workflows.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
